interpretation: The hourglass not done card represents the concept of time running out or a sense of urgency. It reminds us that life is fleeting and we must make the most of every moment. This card may suggest that we need to prioritize our tasks and make efficient use of our time. It can also indicate a need for patience and perseverance, as success may take longer than anticipated. When this card appears, it is a reminder to stay focused and not waste time on trivial matters. It may also indicate that we need to take action before it's too late.
